1
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,680
The medicine is ready.

2
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,740
Then why didn't you bring it earlier?

3
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:15,930
Aunt Huixin.

4
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,970
Paying respects to Your Highness.

5
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,620
Miss Anli is also here.

6
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,760
Her Highness heard that you have trouble moving around,

7
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:30,640
so she ordered me

8
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:32,900
to bring some medicine and supplements.

9
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,280
Her Highness also instructed,

10
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:39,600
hoping Your Highness gets some good rest.

11
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,720
After all, it is not a minor injury,

12
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:42,180
so you must not neglect it.

13
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,400
Thanks to Consort Yu.

14
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,560
When my injury heals,

15
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:48,410
I will definitely pay a visit to thank her.

16
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:53,220
But did I come at a bad time,

17
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:56,250
and delay Your Highness taking the medicine?

18
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:56,960
No.

19
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:59,210
You came at just the right time.

20
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:00,580
This medicine,

21
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,660
combined with some supplements,

22
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,220
will have a better effect.

23
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,920
This medicine is a bit bitter today.

24
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,450
Then I won't disturb your rest.

25
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:18,720
Okay.

26
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,520
Miss Anli, if you have nothing else,

27
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,000
you should go pay respects to Her Highness.

28
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,060
It wouldn't be good

29
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,740
if you broke the rules.

30
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:41,140
Then I will also take my leave.

31
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,120
Okay.

32
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,660
Your Highness,

33
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,050
I will take my leave too.

34
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:24,700
Your Highness.

35
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,740
The princess is delicate,

36
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:29,260
and she has been kneeling for an hour.

37
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:32,080
I think she is very stubborn.

38
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,760
She needs to be polished.

39
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:35,560
Mother.

40
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:40,210
I heard you shouting early in the morning.

41
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,330
What do you want from me?

42
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,159
I missed you, Mother.

43
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:48,090
I came to pay respects to you after seeing Father.

44
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,440
You are not here to see me.

45
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:58,320
You are clearly thinking of someone here.

46
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,760
Your thoughts

47
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,490
are written all over your face.

48
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,240
Nothing escapes your eyes, Mother.

49
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,640
Alright, get up.

50
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:20,180
Thank you, Your Highness.

51
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,260
Thank you, Your Highness.

52
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:27,680
Mother,

53
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,520
then I will take her away.

54
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,240
If Hao'er didn't like her,

55
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,730
I would have sent her away long ago.

56
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,460
Why did Your Highness help me?

57
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,850
Even if you helped me today,

58
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,560
I will not appreciate it.

59
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,240
I don't care if you appreciate it or not.

60
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,880
I only know that as long as I like something,

61
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,940
Mother will definitely get it for me.

62
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:15,080
So no matter if you like me or not,

63
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,600
you will marry me in the future.

64
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,660
But Second Prince,

65
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,200
I am not

66
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,800
an object to be manipulated.

67
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,520
I have the life I want.

68
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,000
Does it make any difference?

69
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,060
This is the palace.

70
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,240
Everyone has to be arranged by others to do things.

71
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,200
Even Father,

72
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,520
what he does and eats every day

73
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,560
is all arranged.

74
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:35,970
What's more,

75
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,080
you were given to me by Mother.

76
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,610
It's enough that I like you.

77
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,620
Since you are not willing,

78
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,140
then forget it.

79
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:08,200
But I don't want to be like Her Highness,

80
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,720
marrying someone I don't love.

81
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:12,800
No matter the outcome,

82
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,200
I, Bai Anli,

83
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,280
will never be

84
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,010
a puppet at the mercy of others.

85
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:33,620
Your Highness,

86
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:34,680
I have checked

87
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,960
the dregs of that medicine.

88
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,120
It is confirmed to be non-toxic.

89
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,560
Good.

90
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,720
Why are you so calm, Your Highness?

91
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,400
Could it be

92
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:44,040
that you knew all along the medicine was non-toxic?

93
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,900
Then why did you ask me to check it?

94
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,240
I wasn't sure

95
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,480
if the medicine was poisoned.

96
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,560
Then why did you drink it during the day?

97
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,040
If something really went wrong,

98
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,970
what would we do?

99
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,580
Huixin arrived so timely,

100
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,680
just to test Ling Xuele.

101
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:00,120
If I didn't play along,

102
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,640
how would Consort Yu feel at ease?

103
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,520
Even so,

104
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:06,180
you shouldn't risk your own life.

105
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,660
Your Highness,

106
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,330
I got this

107
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:14,040
from Miss Zeng Le.

108
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:15,770
While taking it,

109
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:18,320
your pulse will be no different from being poisoned,

110
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:20,240
which should fool them for a while.

111
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:20,680
Good.

112
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:21,940
Your Highness,

113
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,560
it's time for your medicine.

114
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:31,880
Okay.

115
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,039
Your Ladyship,

116
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,299
Eunuch Li just came by.

117
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,890
He said His Majesty ordered

118
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,960
that in a few days,

119
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:44,000
the memorial ceremony for the late Queen

120
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,960
should be held more grandly.

121
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,580
Your Ladyship,

122
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,560
I also heard some rumors

123
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,560
about Queen Yun.

124
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:00,680
It's just gossip

125
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:03,080
from people who like to stir up trouble.

126
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,700
Did you take it seriously?

127
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:07,080
The late Queen liked pear blossoms the most.

128
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:09,140
I heard the female ghost a few days ago

129
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,160
was also wearing pear blossoms.

130
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:13,080
And didn't the First Prince also say

131
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:15,140
that the Queen visited him in a dream?

132
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:17,280
Could it be that she really came back?

133
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,400
Dead is dead.

134
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,760
Someone who has been dead for over a decade

135
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:22,120
can still scare you like this?

136
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:22,880
Useless.

137
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,760
Maybe it's because the late Queen's death anniversary is approaching,

138
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,960
I'm overthinking it.

139
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:30,280
Now, in the palace, those who know about this

140
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,340
are only you and me,

141
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:32,600
no one else.

142
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,980
Even if she really comes back,

143
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,600
I am not afraid.

144
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,560
At worst,

145
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,880
I'll just kill a few more ghosts.

146
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,000
Right now,

147
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:50,200
you should worry most about that girl, Ling Xuele.

148
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:52,040
She is full of tricks.

149
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,660
Keep a close eye on her,

150
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,770
and don't let any mistakes happen.

151
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,600
Rest assured, Your Ladyship,

152
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,000
I have been watching her.

153
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:55,540
Your Highness.

154
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:57,570
Are these Queen Yun's clothes?

155
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,820
Your Highness,

156
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:02,920
yes.

157
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,200
Tonight, wear this

158
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,820
and walk around outside Fengyao Palace.

159
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,580
Your Highness.

160
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,520
Do you think this trick

161
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:19,780
can really make them expose themselves?

162
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:22,640
After all, His Highness has been searching for so long

163
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:23,720
and hasn't found

164
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:26,320
any clues about the truth of Queen Yun's death.

165
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,240
It is exactly because there are no clues

166
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,640
that your help is needed.

167
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,560
What's wrong?

168
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,420
Are you afraid?

169
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,880
Of course not.

170
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:36,530
Don't worry.

171
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,840
I will have Tingfeng accompany you.

172
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:40,440
Yes.

173
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:01,320
Your Majesty.

174
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:02,800
His Highness will be fine.

175
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,040
Please don't worry yourself sick.

176
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,840
Your Majesty, please slow down.

177
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,080
Your Majesty.

178
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:14,560
Father.

179
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,520
Chuan'er, lie down quickly.

180
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:18,000
I am fine.

181
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:19,880
Father, don't worry.

182
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,960
Has the imperial physician

183
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:22,820
come to see you?

184
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,120
To reply to Your Majesty,

185
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,440
the physician has already examined him.

186
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,640
His Highness is fine.

187
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:31,520
It might be that the injury from the previous assassination attempt

188
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:32,580
has not yet healed.

189
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:34,530
He needs to rest for a few more days.

190
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,080
Useless thing!

191
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,330
Why hasn't he recovered after so long?

192
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:43,880
I see

193
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:46,370
you've lost some weight again.

194
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:47,840
Father, don't worry.

195
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:51,960
It might be that I've been taking too much medicine lately,

196
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,920
which has caused a loss of appetite.

197
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:55,580
There is no other discomfort.

198
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,240
I also think His Highness

199
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,520
looks much thinner than a few days ago.

200
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:03,610
Quick, tell the kitchen

201
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:05,720
to prepare more appetizing dishes and send them over.

202
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,880
You must eat more

203
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,410
so you can recover quickly.

204
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:13,080
You were fine a few days ago.

205
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:15,840
Why did you suddenly faint?

206
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,200
A few days ago,

207
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:20,760
I dreamed of Mother.

208
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,610
She said in the dream

209
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:26,220
that she has unfulfilled wishes.

210
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,000
I missed her,

211
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:30,440
so I went to Fengyao Palace to find out.

212
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,160
In a daze,

213
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:34,120
I seemed to see Mother's figure.

214
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,820
I know ghosts and gods are not to be believed,

215
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,080
but perhaps I missed Mother so much

216
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,650
that I had hallucinations.

217
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,400
Then somehow,

218
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:58,330
I suddenly fainted.

219
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,960
Since His Highness is injured,

220
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,480
Since His Highness is injured,

221
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:09,120
you should rest well in the palace.

222
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,920
Don't wander around.

223
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:13,170
Consort Yu is right.

224
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:15,890
Your health is the most important.

225
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,280
As long as your mother

226
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,600
knows your filial piety,

227
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,460
that's enough.

228
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:22,740
Thank you, Father.

229
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,860
Change another physician to examine Chuan'er.

230
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,180
Yes, Your Majesty.

231
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,330
It's been a few days.

232
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:33,000
Why hasn't he gotten better?

233
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:53,880
Consort Yu is really considerate of His Highness.

234
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:57,280
She prepared so much food so quickly.

235
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,280
If you like it,

236
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,160
you can eat it all.

237
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:07,040
It's time to take your medicine.

238
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:16,480
Wait.

239
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,160
Miss Anli.

240
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,580
I asked the physician.

241
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:26,920
About this medicine,

242
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:28,400
if His Highness took it daily,

243
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,600
he would have recovered by now.

244
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,760
Could it be that this medicine

245
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,620
is mixed with other ingredients,

246
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:35,240
keeping His Highness from getting better?

247
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:37,380
You serve His Highness day and night.

248
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,540
You must have poisoned this medicine

249
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:40,600
to murder him.

250
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:45,360
See clearly, Your Highness.

251
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:47,920
I have absolutely no intention of harming you.

252
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:49,980
If you truly have a clear conscience,

253
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:51,640
then drink this medicine.
